ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Tsuu T’ina Nation Reserve No. 145 , Alberta
PrecisOrder setting apart 2,160.275 hectares (5,338.16 acres) of surface land and 2,030.947 hectares (5,018.58 acres) of the mines and minerals underlying those lands for the use and benefit of the Tsuu T’ina Nation as an addition to TSUU T’INA NATION RESERVE NO. 145, located in the Municipality of Rocky View County, Alberta.
